### ============================================
### BASE REQUEST (reuse this header)
### ============================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@contentType = application/json

POST {{baseUrl}}/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "docType": "article_all",
  "docId": "articles",
  "question": "Best sports sedans?",
  "topK": 5
}

### Single article, docId is optional in payload.
POST {{baseUrl}}/articles/motortrend-bmw-m3-2025-review/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "docType": "article",
  "docId": "motortrend-bmw-m3-2025-review",
  "question": "Is the BMW M3 worth the price?",
  "topK": 3,
  "mode": "HYBRID"
}

### Global article search, searching across all articles
POST {{baseUrl}}/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "docType": "article",
  "docId": "articles",
  "question": "Is the BMW M3 worth the price?",
  "topK": 3,
  "mode": "HYBRID"
}

### Article-specific service endpoint, domain-specific, Are you debugging article-only logic?
POST {{baseUrl}}/articles/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Show me articles with ratings over 9 out of 10",
  "topK": 5
}